title: Jaguar Skills
description:
A collection of jaguar skills mixes that are free to download from his blog.  They have been edited to remove Trevor Nelsons blurb before and after each mix

Jaguar Skills is a BBC Radio1/1xtra DJ that mixes on the Trevor Nelson every Saturday at 7:30pm GMT.

To listen over the internet listen at www.bbc.co.uk/radio1
